comment_data.body:
We have different cases here, so let's group them together. The Limited API isn't more special than other reasons to use a different implementation.

commit.message:
Changes CyFunction to compile with Py_LIMITED_API

Mostly that we store the PyCFunctionObject as an attribute of
it rather than "inheriting" from PyCFunctionObject.
